title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 6' game
maintext:
TRENTON, N.J. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the New Jersey Lottery’s “Pick 6” game were:
10-13-29-35-48-49, Xtra: 2
(ten, thirteen, twenty-nine, thirty-five, forty-eight, forty-nine; Xtra: two)
Estimated jackpot: $4.3 million
